∀ (n : ℕ) (a : ℕ → ℤ), (∀ i, ∃ (s₁ s₂ : Finset ℕ), s₁.card = n ∧ s₂.card = n ∧
  s₁ ∩ s₂ = ∅ ∧ s₁ ∪ s₂ = Finset.erase (Finset.range (2 * n + 1)) i ∧
  (s₁.sum a = s₂.sum a)) → ∀ i j, a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ}, (∀ (i : Fin (2 * n + 1)), ∃ (s₁ s₂ : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))),
  s₁.card = n ∧ s₂.card = n ∧ s₁ ∩ s₂ = ∅ ∧ s₁ ∪ s₂ = {j | j ≠ i} ∧ ∑ j in s₁, a j = ∑ j in s₂, a j) →
  ∀ i j : Fin (2 * n + 1), a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i, ∃ (s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))), s.card = n ∧ ∑ j in s, a j = ∑ j in (Finset.univ \ s), a j) →
  ∀ i j, a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i, ∃ (s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))), s.card = n ∧ i ∉ s ∧ s.sum (fun j => a j) = Finset.univ \ {i}.sum (fun j => a j)) →
    ∀ i j, a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i : Fin (2 * n + 1),
    ∃ (s t : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))),
      s.card = n ∧ t.card = n ∧ s ∪ t = Finset.univ.erase i ∧ s.sum a = t.sum a) →
  ∀ i j : Fin (2 * n + 1), a i = a j

∀ {a : ℕ → ℤ} {n : ℕ}, (∀ i, ∃ (s t : Finset ℕ) (hs : s.card = n) (ht : t.card = n), s ∪ t = (Finset.range (2 * n + 1)).erase i ∧ (Finset.sum s fun x => a x) = (Finset.sum t fun x => a x)) → ∀ i j, a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ (i : Fin (2 * n + 1)), ∃ (s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))), s.card = n ∧ (s \ {i}).sum a = (sᶜ \ {i}).sum a) →
  ∀ (i j : Fin (2 * n + 1)), a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i : Fin (2 * n + 1), ∃ (s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1))),
    s.card = n ∧ (∑ j in s, a j) = ∑ j in sᶜ, a j) →
    ∀ i j : Fin (2 * n + 1), a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i : Fin (2 * n + 1), ∃ s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1)), s.card = n ∧ i ∉ s ∧ ∑ x in s, a x = ∑ x in Finset.univ.sdiff s \ {i}, a x) →
  ∀ i j : Fin (2 * n + 1), a i = a j

∀ {n : ℕ} {a : Fin (2 * n + 1) → ℤ},
  (∀ i, ∃ s : Finset (Fin (2 * n + 1)), s.card = n ∧ (s.sum a = (Finset.univ \ {i}).sum a)) →
  ∀ i j, a i = a j
